                            <comment id="12875078" author="knutanders" created="Thu, 3 Jun 2010 12:14:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached is a patch that adds a test case to the T_b2i test and some debug code to release the latch in BTreeScan. When running the test with sane jars, it fails with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ERROR XSAM6: Record &lt;/p&gt;
{2}
&lt;p&gt; on page 7 in container 625 not found.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12875622" author="knutanders" created="Fri, 4 Jun 2010 15:07:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The attached patch (derby-4083-1a.diff) contains the test and debug changes, and also adds the missing negation that&apos;s required for the code to work. All the regression tests ran cleanly with this patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12876157" author="knutanders" created="Mon, 7 Jun 2010 08:09:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed revision 952131.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t think this code path can be reached without using the store API directly, so I&apos;m not planning to back-port the fix for now. Closing the issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
